data.description: Stunning Eagle Ridge Home just hit the market in Pueblo!! This beautiful home features 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and 1,088 sq. ft of living space. The main level features a bright and spacious living room with tile floors, tons of natural sunlight and a gas fireplace. The kitchen is steps away and comes equipped with stainless steel appliances, generously sized pantry and dining area. The upper level features three spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom. This home is also equipped with solar panels, giving you eco-friendly energy and potential savings on your electrical bills. Enjoy quick commutes Fort Carson while also being near shopping, dining and entertainment. – This home shows true pride of ownership, come see it today!
